data.description: Tuscany Preserve Is a Resort Style Guard Gated Community. Beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2 Car Garage with Screen Porch. The property is versatile in its usage, allowing for short-term rentals, long-term leasing, or serving as a primary residence. The community offers a range of amenities, including a pool, tennis courts, basketball courts, fitness center, recreation room, and a playground.  The home features a clay tile roof and a brick paver driveway, adding to its visual appeal. Inside, there have been several updates, including a new kitchen with wood cabinets, granite countertops, and a stylish backsplash. The entire house boasts new tile flooring. The master bathroom has been remodeled with a new shower, and both bathrooms have new toilets. Additionally, the back screen patio has undergone a remodel. The air conditioning unit was replaced in 2019.  Residents of the community can enjoy the convenience of lawn maintenance being taken care of by the Homeowners Association (HOA), along with basic cable services and access to all the mentioned amenities. Poinciana, the surrounding area, provides additional parks, pools, and amenities for residents' use. A hospital is located just minutes away, as well as a shopping center.  In summary, this property offers a well-maintained and updated home in a secure and amenity-rich community. Whether you're looking for a primary residence, a vacation rental, or an investment property, this home in Tuscany Preserve could be a great fit. Contact for appointments and further details.
